title: Naisho no Kyouko-neesan
original_name: ないしょの京子姉さん
sinopse:
Kyouko is the strongest delinquent in school, but she has a secret: she loves her little brother Ayumu! She can't let anyone know or else her reputation would be ruined, but he's so cute that it takes all her strength just to hold herself back.

(Source: Shogakukan, translated)
